track_notes: LIke SC-003 Beacon Batch - a 20 minute walk. This time through a wood and cow field (beasts present July 2014 - no hassle from the beasts). I returned by dropping down the side of the hill to the lower path and walked back along the road - not recommended due to quite high traffic levels and no quicker than the way up was anyway...
